name: The ghost of the Collet House 04
description: This is the story of a beautiful ghost that haunts the Victorian house where the Collet family lives. She still does not know that she has died and that is why she is still there, living in the memory of her family.Esta es la historia de una bella fantasma que ronda la casa victoriana en la que vive la familia Collet. Ella todavía no sabe que ha muerto y es por eso que sigue ahí, habitando en el recuerdo de su familia
